F. C. BELDEN v. TOWN OF LAKE PARK (formerly Kelsey City), a municipal corporation of Florida. 23 So. (2nd) 735

June Term, 1945

November 16, 1945 Division A A. R. Roebuck and John Ziegler, for appellant. Edward G. Newell, for appellee. PER CURIAM:

Affirmed on the authority of McPherson v. Town of Lake Maitland, 134 Fla. 720, 184 So. 487.

CHAPMAN, C. J., TERRELL, BROWN, BUFORD, THOMAS, ADAMS and SEBRING, JJ., concur.
